reviewText: TD Jakes gives us the kind of spiritual guidance we all need each and every day.  Thank God for filling him with the holy spirit and anointing to do his work.

I MAY NOT BE QUALIFIED TO REVIEW SOMEONE LIKE
T.D. JAKES SINCE HE ALONE WOULD BE THE EXPERT
ON WHAT HE IS TRYING TO SAY-- I  LOVE HIS MESSAGES
FOR THAT REASON I GAVE IT A 3 I FELT LIKE SOME OF HIS
OTHER MESSAGES HAVE BEEN BETTER,. EVERY THING
WAS IN GOOD CONDITION-
This is a fantastic message that reminds us not to allow our own restriction to inhibit our purpose but propel us onward and forward. God is for us.

This sermon has been one of the biggest blessings.  T.D. Jakes speaks about stepping out of the box of your comfort zone, trusting God and stepping into the UNKNOWN....I randomly purchased this DVD, and realized after watching this, that it was another sign from God leading to one of the biggest life changing decisions I had to make.  It was a career decision that I had to make to MOVE toward my destiny.  This DVD encouraged me and allowed me step out of my comfort zone and walk with God, trusting Him to guide me toward my blessing!  If you need a life changing experience and an answer to making a big career decision, etc., purchase this DVD NOW!!!!
I will recommend this dvd to my friends.  It has been very inspirational to me and I will continue to purchase Bishop Jakes products.  Thanks Bishop.
I thought it was going to be him talking but It was just like attending his church. Not worth the money. I probibly could have just watched it on YouTube.

Great video.  The Bishop has always been on the right track in his speaking.  This video is a nice one to add to your collection.  It's one to pick up when you've been to church but didn't get enough church for that day.  If you need uplifting at anytime of the day or night.  This is worth the purchase.

I watched this four times and then blessed two friends with it. When T.D. Jakes says: "It takes a radical person...", it's exhilarting to see that Jakes is an awesome and amazing role model. Praise the Lord!
I love everyting TD Jakes does, he such an encourager.
Very inspirational.
we will always have restrictions but this cd tells us how to live with those restriction by what the word of God say'.
Love the item. Functions as described/designed and I am satisified.  I would purchase this item again and I would recommend it to anyone.

THIS SERMON IS BY FAR ONE OF THE BEST BLESSINGS IN MY LIFE,MY LORD HEARING MY CRY'S. EVERY POWERFUL WORD HE SPEAKS JUST PULLS ME IN CLOSER TO MY GOD. I DON'T KNOW WHAT I WAS WAITING ON OR WHY IT TOOK ME SO LONG TO REALIZE HE IS THE ANSWER TO EVERYTHING. I'M ON MY WAY!!!!! BUY THE DVD IT WILL CHANGE YOUR LIFE.I BUY EVERYONE I CAN GET MY HANDS ON.THIS DVD IS VERY UPLIFTING AND ENCOURAGING.THE SERMONS TRULY SPEAKS TO MY SOUL.
Bishop Jakes was phenomenal in this, so I had to purchase a copy for myself. A must-have for anyone living with boundaries.

I would highly recommend this sermon.  I have and I am still enjoyong it.  This is surely a keepsake.  I have always found his sermon very insightful and he is  an excellent teacher.  I have no regrets in purchasing this product and I would encourage everyone who is seeking to understand the will of God and the different avenues we travel on our journey to fullfilling God's calling on our lives.
Oh my I absolutely love love his sermon it truly speaks to my soul. I actually feel like a better person when I listened to him God bless this Man.
Really enjoy listening to him speak. Very positive and uplifting words of encourage. Very powerful and touching. Really enjoy this
The product itself is defective.  This one also pauses and appears to be in slow motion.  It also stops before the ending.

All of Bishop Jake's material is one size fits ALL!! The Word of God NEVER fails. If you use the techniques in the Word and really allow what Bishop Jake's is teaching to dwell in you heart and mind, God will change you and He is using this man of God as a vessel to deliver His message in a plain, simple and unique way!!!
